name: Sea Jet Ski Drive 3D
description:
Go on the joy ride of a lifetime with an awesome jet ski and feel the rush of the cool sea. Riding a jet ski is always immensely fun and exciting.
Features:
• 30 levels with different stunts to perform and complete
• Cool Jet Skis to ride
• Achieve additional points for being timely
• Outstanding controls for steering and riding the Jet Ski
